metadata.name: Temple of the Golden Pavilion
metadata.description:
Reflection of Kinkaku-ji in HDR. 
(金閣寺),Temple of the Golden Pavilion, is a Zen Buddhist temple in Kyoto, Japan.

Taken using Canon EOS 6D & Canon EF 16-35mm f/2.8L II USM
https://www.flickr.com/photos/qqjawe/8842241863/in/album-72157633712806157/
